Summary: Light in sky. My daughter said it was moving faster than what a plane could move
divs: Sighting DetailsMy daughter was on her way to work this morning in Houston and saw this in the sky. She took the pic and sent it to me. It would seem like it was a plane--but given the fact that her and I keep up on UFO news, she said she didn't think it was a plane and so I felt I should report it.
trends: There have been 173 other sightings in Houston
There were no other sightings in Houston on or around October 9th 2013
